cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NA, cs.IT, cs.MM

The paper proposes a deep learning approach for diffuse optical tomography, which involves image reconstruction and analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of deep neural networks, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves mathematical theory and numerical methods, which could place it in cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) and cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper involves the use of a prototype DOT system, which suggests that it could belong to cs.MM (Multimedia).
